cu.explanation_en: Setting the integrity algorithm to the unknown enum 'nia9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the MAC log level to an invalid enum value will cause logging configuration errors and potentially prevent proper MAC layer initialization.
du.explanation_zh: 將 MAC 日誌級別設定為無效的枚舉值會導致日誌配置錯誤，並可能阻止正確的 MAC 層初始化。
